NAME
       atktopbm - convert Andrew Toolkit raster object to PBM


SYNOPSIS
       atktopbm [atkfile]


DESCRIPTION
       This program is part of Netpbm(1).

       atktopbm reads an Andrew Toolkit raster object as input.
       and produces a PBM image as output.

       pbmtoatk(1), pbm(1)
